INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2014-10-08 20:27:53','2014-10-08 20:27:53','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','trash','open','open','','hello-world','','','2014-10-13 18:50:40','2014-10-13 18:50:40','',0,'http://airstream.uc01.clc.af.cm/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2014-10-08 20:27:53','2014-10-08 20:27:53','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">I work in IT and have too many hobbies.\r\nThis site is an attempt to document my project of refurbishing an 1978 Excella 500 31\' Airstream travel trailer.</p>\r\n<a href=\"http://github.com/peterolivo\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://res.cloudinary.com/hpuomxzff/image/upload/v1413577600/Programming-Github-icon_befepn.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></a><a href=\"http://twitter.com/peterolivo\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-37\" src=\"http://res.cloudinary.com/hpuomxzff/image/upload/v1413577846/twitter-5-xl_coomaa.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></a>','About Page','','publish','open','open','','sample-page','','','2014-10-17 20:34:38','2014-10-17 20:34:38','',0,'http://airstream.uc01.clc.af.cm/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(4,1,'2014-10-08 20:38:17','2014-10-08 20:38:17','','aistream','','inherit','open','open','','aistream','','','2014-10-08 20:38:17','2014-10-08 20:38:17','',0,'http://airstream.uc01.clc.af.cm/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/aistream.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5,1,'2014-10-13 17:18:36','2014-10-13 17:18:36','','aistream','','inherit','open','open','','aistream-2','','','2014-10-13 17:18:36','2014-10-13 17:18:36','',0,'http://airstream.uc01.clc.af.cm/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/aistream.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(6,1,'2014-10-13 17:18:49','2014-10-13 17:18:49','','aistream','','inherit','open','open','','aistream-3','','','2014-10-13 17:18:49','2014-10-13 17:18:49','',0,'http://airstream.uc01.clc.af.cm/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/aistream1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(7,1,'2014-10-13 18:04:39','2014-10-13 18:04:39','','aistream','','inherit','open','open','','aistream-4','','','2014-10-13 18:04:39','2014-10-13 18:04:39','',0,'http://airstream.uc01.clc.af.cm/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/aistream.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(8,1,'2014-10-13 18:45:20','2014-10-13 18:45:20','','aistream','','inherit','open','open','','aistream-5','','','2014-10-13 18:45:20','2014-10-13 18:45:20','',0,'http://airstream.uc01.clc.af.cm/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/aistream.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(9,1,'2014-10-13 18:45:29','2014-10-13 18:45:29','','aistream','','inherit','open','open','','aistream-6','','','2014-10-13 18:45:29','2014-10-13 18:45:29','',0,'http://airstream.uc01.clc.af.cm/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/aistream.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(10,1,'2014-10-13 18:50:40','2014-10-13 18:50:40','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','inherit','open','open','','1-revision-v1','','','2014-10-13 18:50:40','2014-10-13 18:50:40','',1,'http://airstream.uc01.clc.af.cm/?p=10',0,'revision','',0),(11,1,'2014-10-13 19:29:53','2014-10-13 19:29:53','The journey has begun.\r\n\r\nI recently purchased a 1978 Excella 500 31\' Airstream trailer. My dreams of creating a tiny live and work space are finally coming to a start. I have often dreamed of a tiny house, living simply and creating a space that can be moved as I journey through life. Working in the tech industry has provided me a grounded basis in ephemeral nature of worldly objects, i.e. I have very little of them. Things I keep are often highly deliberated or passed along for others to enjoy. I plan to create a space where I can harbor these selections and not feel cluttered or intruded upon as large spaces can do. I am excited to clear and re-purpose this trailer into just that. This blog will be stream of consciousness, with the progress of the trailer and related information that is relevant to the progress such as drawings, updates, etc.\r\n\r\nSpeaking of etc. here is a sweet Airstream patch.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-14 aligncenter\" src=\"http://res.cloudinary.com/hpuomxzff/image/upload/c_scale,w_250/v1413228456/airstreamlogo_v9mrup.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"246\" />\r\n\r\nEdit: Here is a sweet picture of the trailer courtesy of a friend.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0IwBtLLl.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" /></p>','Airstream Journey','','publish','open','open','','airstream-journey','','','2014-10-28 20:56:46','2014-10-28 20:56:46','',0,'http://airstream.uc01.clc.af.cm/?p=11',0,'post','',0),(12,1,'2014-10-13 19:28:05','2014-10-13 19:28:05','','airstreamlogo_v9mrup','','inherit','open','open','','airstreamlogo_v9mrup','','','2014-10-13 19:28:05','2014-10-13 19:28:05','',11,'http://res.cloudinary.com/hpuomxzff/image/upload/c_scale,w_350/v1413228456/airstreamlogo_v9mrup.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(13,1,'2014-10-13 19:28:16','2014-10-13 19:28:16','The journey has begun.\r\n\r\nI recently purchased a 1978 Excella 500 31\' Airstream trailer. My dreams of creating a tiny live and work space are finally coming to a start. I have often dreamed of a tiny house, living simply and creating a space that can be moved as I journey through life. Working in the tech industry has provided me a grounded basis in ephemeral nature of worldly objects, i.e. I have very little of them. Things I keep are often highly deliberated or passed along for others to enjoy. I plan to create a space where I can harbor these selections and not feel cluttered or intruded upon as large spaces can do. I am excited to clear and re-purpose this trailer into just that. This blog will be stream of consciousness, with the progress of the trailer and related information that is relevant to the progress such as drawings, updates, etc.\r\n\r\nSpeaking of etc. here is a sweet Airstream patch.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-12\" src=\"